Node implementing the teleoperation of the Shadow arm via a 6DOF pose sensor and a Cartesian Pose Controller. To use, move the arm in a appropriate inital posture, e.g., via:

rostopic pub /sr_arm/sendupdate sr_robot_msgs/sendupdate "{sendupdate_length: 4 ,sendupdate_list:
[{joint_name: ElbowJRotate,joint_target: 45},{joint_name: ElbowJSwing,joint_target: 60},{joint_name:
ShoulderJRotate,joint_target: 0},{joint_name: ShoulderJSwing,joint_target: 30}]}"

and call the /start_teleop service. This service will synchronize the pose of the tracked link expressed in the given base frame and the pose of the sensor in the emitter frame. Parameters are specified in the /robot/config.yaml file. 

